Get the IP Address of guvi.in:
 $ ping guvi.in
Find the CPU/Memory usage of the server:
 $ top
Test the connectivity between 2 nodes:
 $ netstat
To Check the list of ports:
 $ nmap guvi.in
To check the status of the port:
 $ telnet guvi.in 9000
O/P link: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1XXiFNler-5ecYf5ETBd8vMQC7NU1UPU9
